Xiao Yan!

25
00:02:00,760 --> 00:02:03,000
Are you done with this nonsense?

26
00:02:03,190 --> 00:02:05,510
You deceived the superiors
and subordinates,

27
00:02:05,510 --> 00:02:08,240
