of the entire Academy for your own good.

28
00:02:09,750 --> 00:02:10,590
Bai Cheng.

29
00:02:12,110 --> 00:02:14,600
You made Xiao Yan
savor the pain of loss

30
00:02:14,600 --> 00:02:15,750
and ruined his reputation,

31
00:02:16,720 --> 00:02:19,080
all of which can soothe
the hatred in your heart?

32
00:02:22,110 --> 00:02:24,160
How are you going to repay

33
00:02:24,360 --> 00:02:25,750
the innocent lives who died in the tower?

34
00:02:27,470 --> 00:02:29,720
What will you do

35
00:02:29,730 --> 00:02:31,640
when their families and friends
are coming for you?

36
00:02:33,110 --> 00:02:34,240
And you.

37
00:02:37,440 --> 00:02:38,910
How dare you

38
00:02:40,390 --> 00:02:42,830
let Little Fairy Doctor in the tower?

39
00:02:44,110 --> 00:02:45,960
Are you taking my words lightly?

40
00:02:50,670 --> 00:02:53,270
I'll take the punishment voluntarily.

41
00:03:25,880 --> 00:03:28,550
Solidified space,
the Dou Ancestor-level technique?

42
00:03:36,320 --> 00:03:38,030
As long as Xiao Yan knows
that we are fine,

43
00:03:39,270 --> 00:03:40,240
he will be calm.

44
