Little Fairy Doctor's Woeful Poison Body
doesn't seem to have broken out.

45
00:03:51,000 --> 00:03:52,000
In the eyes of the world,

46
00:03:54,030 --> 00:03:55,750
a person with Woeful Poison Body
is ominous.

47
00:03:57,960 --> 00:04:00,030
But is Woeful Poison Body
the only ominous one?

48
00:04:03,030 --> 00:04:04,390
When I first came to the Academy,

49
00:04:05,910 --> 00:04:08,360
it was widely known that I was
being hunted by Misty Cloud Sect.

50
00:04:10,750 --> 00:04:12,830
In the Jia Ma Empire,
I was an ominous person.

51
00:04:15,630 --> 00:04:17,350
But the Academy didn't reject me.

52
00:04:19,000 --> 00:04:20,000
Why is that?

53
00:04:22,200 --> 00:04:24,390
The Misty Cloud Sect
was chasing me everywhere.

54
00:04:25,670 --> 00:04:28,480
But the Academy still lent me
Heavenly Flames to fight the enemy.

55
00:04:29,880 --> 00:04:30,950
Why?

56
00:04:35,510 --> 00:04:37,790
Because the Academy never
makes its own judgments

57
00:04:37,790 --> 00:04:38,950
based on outside voices.

58
00:04:41,320 --> 00:04:43,000
They reject neither the gifted ones

59
00:04:44,550 --> 00:04:46,270
nor the destitute.

60
00:04:48,320 --> 00:04:50,000
They do not submit
to monstrous forces,

61
00:04:50,950 --> 00:04:52,600
nor do they fawn on supreme force.

62
00:04:54,390 --> 00:04:55,320
Jia Nan Academy

63
00:04:55,320 --> 00:04:56,830
has its own justice and beliefs.

64
00:05:01,780 --> 00:05:02,670
That's why

65
00:05:02,670 --> 00:05:05,160
when Little Fairy Doctor was about
to have her Woeful Poison Body explode,

66
00:05:05,480 --> 00:05:07,440
I chose to return
to Jia Nan Academy for the first time.

67
00:05:11,480 --> 00:05:12,550
I believe

68
00:05:13,040 --> 00:05:14,230
the Academy will accept her,

69
00:05:15,160 --> 00:05:16,720
just as it accepted me
in the first place.

70
00:05:20,940 --> 00:05:22,270
Once the Woeful Poison Body
breaks out,

71
00:05:22,270 --> 00:05:23,670
the entire Academy
will be destroyed,

72
00:05:23,920 --> 00:05:24,830
not just us.

73
00:05:26,160 --> 00:05:27,000
Xiao Yan never takes

74
00:05:27,000 --> 00:05:28,480
everyone's life seriously.

75
00:05:29,110 --> 00:05:30,510
If you hadn't deliberately set it up,

76
00:05:31,320 --> 00:05:32,880
she couldn't have broken out
so early.

77
00:05:33,950 --> 00:05:35,510
It's pointless to talk about this now.

78
00:05:36,920 --> 00:05:38,160
Even if she's fine now,

79
00:05:38,510 --> 00:05:40,040
Woeful Poison Body has no cure.

80
00:05:40,720 --> 00:05:42,000
She is ultimately a hidden danger.

81
00:05:42,600 --> 00:05:43,440
I can solve it.

82
00:05:44,390 --> 00:05:45,230
You're lying.

83
00:05:45,720 --> 00:05:47,670
There is simply no solution
in this world

84
00:05:47,670 --> 00:05:48,950
for the Woeful Poison Body.

85
00:05:49,320 --> 00:05:50,160
Yes, there is.

86
00:05:51,320 --> 00:05:52,160
Headmaster.

87
00:05:52,720 --> 00:05:53,880
Woeful Poison Body

88
00:05:54,550 --> 00:05:55,920
does have a cure.

89
00:05:57,200 --> 00:05:59,040
It is just that this medicine
is so difficult to find

90
00:06:00,160 --> 00:06:01,000
that the world

91
00:06:02,270 --> 00:06:04,830
regards the Woeful Poison Body
as an incurable poison.

92
00:06:07,390 --> 00:06:08,830
I'm just gonna need some time.

93
00:06:09,480 --> 00:06:10,480
Please allow me, Headmaster.

94
00:06:12,040 --> 00:06:13,000
Please allow him, Headmaster.

95
00:06:13,600 --> 00:06:14,880
Please allow him, Headmaster.

96
00:06:17,320 --> 00:06:18,160
Ridiculous.

97
00:06:19,920 --> 00:06:22,390
