to look for the antidote?

98
00:06:23,110 --> 00:06:25,000
If you can't find it
for the rest of your life,

99
00:06:25,050 --> 00:06:25,950
the Woeful Poison Body

100
00:06:25,950 --> 00:06:27,670
will have to stay
in Jia Nan Academy forever?

101
00:06:29,200 --> 00:06:30,560
I'm at the Headmaster's command

102
00:06:31,000 --> 00:06:32,670
as to the period of finding the antidote.

103
00:06:36,830 --> 00:06:38,760
What if you can't find the solution

104
00:06:39,200 --> 00:06:40,640
by the end of that time?

105
00:06:41,510 --> 00:06:42,850
Or what if the Woeful Poison Body

106
00:06:43,640 --> 00:06:45,200
suddenly breaks out?

107
00:06:48,550 --> 00:06:51,070
Then I'll die
with the Woeful Poison Body

108
00:06:52,320 --> 00:06:53,480
in the Heavenly Flames.

109
00:07:13,880 --> 00:07:15,550
She can absorb the poison mist

110
00:07:15,880 --> 00:07:16,950
inside the Solidified Space.

111
00:07:34,720 --> 00:07:35,640
Your friend

112
00:07:37,040 --> 00:07:39,350
can take temporary shelter
in the Blazing Sky Qi Refining Tower.

113
00:07:42,320 --> 00:07:43,670
I'll decide on the duration

114
00:07:43,950 --> 00:07:45,270
depending on the situation.

115
00:07:46,320 --> 00:07:47,160
Thank you, Headmaster.

116
00:07:47,450 --> 00:07:48,320
Headmaster.

117
00:07:48,350 --> 00:07:49,350
During this period,

118
00:07:50,000 --> 00:07:51,920
I'll keep the Academy safe.

119
00:07:52,880 --> 00:07:53,830
This matter is settled,

120
00:07:54,670 --> 00:07:55,910
no need for further discussion.

121
00:08:10,350 --> 00:08:11,230
What are you going to do

122
00:08:11,880 --> 00:08:13,230
