124
00:08:16,790 --> 00:08:18,070
She won't lose control.

125
00:08:18,270 --> 00:08:19,830
She almost broke out just now,

126
00:08:20,000 --> 00:08:21,480
but suddenly withdrew
her poison mist.

127
00:08:21,950 --> 00:08:23,950
If it's really as described
in the ancient books,

128
00:08:24,480 --> 00:08:25,760
the pain of withdrawing poison mist

129
00:08:26,110 --> 00:08:27,720
is far more than killing herself.

130
00:08:28,270 --> 00:08:30,640
