the poison mist?

131
00:08:32,760 --> 00:08:33,840
Dying is easy.

132
00:08:34,960 --> 00:08:36,350
But if I die here today,

133
00:08:36,790 --> 00:08:39,470
the Blazing Sky Qi Refining Tower
will be abandoned as a result,

134
00:08:41,080 --> 00:08:43,080
and Xiao Yan will regret his decision

135
00:08:43,350 --> 00:08:45,230
to bring me into the tower
for the rest of his life.

136
00:08:45,230 --> 00:08:46,590
I don't want him
to live with such remorse.

137
00:08:47,400 --> 00:08:48,790
You are so young

138
00:08:49,840 --> 00:08:51,910
