145
00:09:37,200 --> 00:09:38,670
You don't have to stay.

146
00:09:44,880 --> 00:09:46,590
It's all thanks
to Little Fairy Doctor's patience

147
00:09:47,880 --> 00:09:49,640
that you were able to leave
safe and sound.

148
00:09:51,030 --> 00:09:51,870
Don't be reckless

149
00:09:52,640 --> 00:09:53,670
next time.

150
00:10:01,400 --> 00:10:03,440
I wish you good luck.

151
00:10:04,710 --> 00:10:05,550
May you

152
00:10:06,440 --> 00:10:07,910
have no regrets.

153
00:10:08,670 --> 00:10:09,510
Thank you, Headmaster.

154
00:10:26,320 --> 00:10:27,230
Thank you for today.

155
00:10:29,110 --> 00:10:29,950
There's no rush.

156
00:10:30,200 --> 00:10:31,200
We're not done yet.

157
00:10:31,240 --> 00:10:32,990
We'll settle the score together
when you get back.

158
00:10:34,400 --> 00:10:35,240
Your Highness.

159
00:10:35,670 --> 00:10:37,320
I know I owe you more and more.

160
00:10:39,840 --> 00:10:40,680
Little Fairy Doctor.

161
00:10:41,230 --> 00:10:42,110
Stay here in peace.

162
00:10:42,670 --> 00:10:44,550
I'll bring back the Bodhisattva Saliva.

163
00:10:50,760 --> 00:10:51,710
Be careful

164
00:10:52,110 --> 00:10:52,950
