what you owe me.

167
00:10:57,080 --> 00:10:57,960
Got it, Your Highness.

168
00:11:13,640 --> 00:11:14,480
Bai Cheng.

169
00:11:15,470 --> 00:11:18,230
Xiao Yan broke the academy rules

170
00:11:18,350 --> 00:11:20,440
by bringing the Woeful Poison Body
into the tower privately.

171
00:11:20,760 --> 00:11:22,590
You laid an ambush inside the tower,

172
00:11:22,910 --> 00:11:25,400
induced the Poison Body without regard
for the safety of the Academy,

173
00:11:26,000 --> 00:11:27,910
