187
00:12:13,200 --> 00:12:15,400
or make a request to the Academy.

188
00:12:16,590 --> 00:12:18,550
As long as it doesn't touch
the Academy's bottom line,

189
00:12:19,230 --> 00:12:21,000
the Academy has to agree.

190
00:12:23,110 --> 00:12:24,150
But now

191
00:12:24,670 --> 00:12:26,110
Xiao Yan has to first

192
00:12:26,760 --> 00:12:28,280
find Bodhisattva Saliva.

193
00:12:29,710 --> 00:12:30,550
