194
00:12:31,710 --> 00:12:32,550
When I return,

195
00:12:33,320 --> 00:12:34,160
I'll be there to fight.

196
00:12:34,200 --> 00:12:35,040
I'll be waiting.

197
00:12:53,150 --> 00:12:53,990
Mu Gu.

198
00:13:03,670 --> 00:13:04,790
Jia Nan Academy

199
00:13:05,350 --> 00:13:06,710
won't allow you to act recklessly.

200
00:13:08,880 --> 00:13:10,840
My target today is Xiao Yan,

201
00:13:11,000 --> 00:13:12,440
