with all of you.

202
00:13:13,080 --> 00:13:14,670
If you have to interfere,

203
00:13:14,960 --> 00:13:16,550
don't blame me for being rude.

204
00:13:16,960 --> 00:13:17,800
Mu Gu.

205
00:13:18,200 --> 00:13:19,230
I was just coming to get you.

206
00:13:19,840 --> 00:13:20,980
