and I'm a Dou Emperor.

215
00:13:39,320 --> 00:13:40,400
That's a huge gap.

216
00:13:40,880 --> 00:13:42,440
It would be a tough battle.

217
00:13:42,640 --> 00:13:43,880
But we have to fight.

218
00:13:53,520 --> 00:13:55,350
