219
00:13:56,000 --> 00:13:58,280
It's your turn today.

220
00:15:00,320 --> 00:15:01,350
Dou Qi protection.

221
00:15:10,000 --> 00:15:10,840
Little Fairy Doctor.

222
00:15:15,640 --> 00:15:16,980
Five-snake Poison Brake Seal.

223
00:15:17,400 --> 00:15:18,240
Active!

224
00:15:25,520 --> 00:15:26,550
This black Dou Qi

225
00:15:28,150 --> 00:15:29,520
is the same as Han Feng's aura.

226
00:15:30,520 --> 00:15:31,800
