can only temporarily guarantee

230
00:15:39,520 --> 00:15:41,470
that she won't be induced
by the source of the poison.

231
00:15:41,550 --> 00:15:42,390
I'm not sure

232
00:15:44,470 --> 00:15:45,310
how long it will last.

233
00:15:52,670 --> 00:15:55,000
I could tell in the battle
at the Misty Cloud Sect

234
00:15:55,790 --> 00:15:58,520
that you needed time
to mobilize the Three-colored Flame Lotus.

235
00:15:59,230 --> 00:16:02,150
