Heavy Black Ruler to resist,

236
00:16:02,150 --> 00:16:04,110
but you were actually mobilizing
your Dou Qi in secret.

237
00:16:04,520 --> 00:16:05,640
After this trick has been used once

238
00:16:06,030 --> 00:16:07,640
in front of me,

239
00:16:08,640 --> 00:16:10,590
