with Green Lotus Core Flame?

244
00:16:57,400 --> 00:17:00,960
Fallen Heart Flame can stand on its own.

245
00:17:01,230 --> 00:17:02,070
Who is that?

246
00:17:07,000 --> 00:17:08,590
(If you use it like this,)

247
00:17:08,710 --> 00:17:12,160
(how is Fallen Heart Flame any different
from other Heavenly Flames?)

248
00:17:16,590 --> 00:17:17,880
(Think about the characteristics)

249
00:17:18,070 --> 00:17:20,350
(of Fallen Heart Flame.)

250
00:17:20,680 --> 00:17:23,470
(Use your brain and think about it.)

251
00:17:24,950 --> 00:17:26,560
Who is it? So annoying.

252
00:17:28,430 --> 00:17:29,270
Brat.

253
00:17:30,160 --> 00:17:31,000
Get down here!

254
00:17:32,590 --> 00:17:33,430
Get down here!

255
00:17:41,040 --> 00:17:41,880
Xiao Yan.

256
00:17:43,590 --> 00:17:44,430
Xiao Yan.

257
00:18:26,640 --> 00:18:27,560
Observe the way of heaven.

258
00:18:28,000 --> 00:18:29,000
Perform the acts of Heaven.

259
00:18:29,560 --> 00:18:31,430
Don't show your face
and dissolve the strife.

260
00:18:31,880 --> 00:18:33,560
Harmonize the light
and mix with the world.

261
00:18:38,110 --> 00:18:39,520
Where are the Protector Elders?

262
00:18:49,230 --> 00:18:50,950
Protector Elders?

263
00:18:51,640 --> 00:18:53,950
Nine Dou Kings together are perfect.

264
00:18:54,710 --> 00:18:57,070
Your Dou Qi will be offered
to the Hall of Souls.

265
00:18:58,640 --> 00:19:00,470
Nine-star Shelter Formation.

266
00:19:06,000 --> 00:19:08,400
This is the opening formation
of Jia Nan Academy.

267
00:19:08,710 --> 00:19:09,830
It uses the sky as a hut,

268
00:19:09,830 --> 00:19:12,640
drawing in the energy of the universe
to introduce into itself,

269
00:19:12,920 --> 00:19:14,040
and can superimpose energy

270
